title: Number of outbound trips from Brazil to Europe in 2018 , by region of destination
summary: This chart shows the Number outbound on Brazil in millions 2.23 .

\\n From the chart we see that Central/Eastern_Europe outbound a total of £ 2.23 millions for the year , £ 120 millions more than the closest competitor ( Southern/Mediterranean_Europe , which outbound £ 2.23 millions ) and over twice as much Western_Europe and Northern_Europe put together ( which outbound £ 1.63 and £ 0.26 millions respectively , totalling £ 150 millions ) .
gold: This statistic shows the number of outbound trips from Brazil to Europe in 2018 , by region of destination . There were approximately 2.23 million trips from Brazil to Southern and Mediterranean Europe in 2018 .
